## 2026-03-27 - Build-time "Cannot access 'X' before initialization" TDZ errors — audit circular dependencies with madge and break cycles
- Ran `madge --circular` on all three packages (figma-plugin, core, server) — no circular dependencies found.
- Found the actual TDZ risk: `colorUtils.ts` imported `hexToLab` and `labToHex` from `@tokenmanager/core`, creating a cross-module dependency in the singlefile bundle. Since `colorUtils.ts` already had `toLinear`, `fromLinear`, `rgbToLab`, `hexToRgb`, and `rgbToHex` defined locally, added inline implementations of `hexToLab` and `labToHex` and removed the `@tokenmanager/core` import entirely.
- Files changed: `packages/figma-plugin/src/ui/shared/colorUtils.ts` ~L53

